# libs/spec-kit

- One Zod schema per `taskType` documented in `docs/specs/tasks/`
- Export schema registry used by API (`ai`, `tasks`) for validation whitelist
- AI may only emit registered `taskType` values
- No imports from `apps/*` or `libs/integrations/*`

When adding a task:

1. Add `docs/specs/tasks/<name>.md`
2. Implement Zod in spec-kit
3. Register in task type enum / registry
4. Update `docs/specs/tasks/README.md`
